## 6. Hardware Donations and Sponsorship

The SLATE project accepts hardware donations to expand local AI processing capabilities. Accepted donations include but are not limited to:

- NVIDIA DGX systems and enterprise GPUs
- High-performance compute hardware
- Storage and networking equipment
- Cloud compute credits for CI/CD (not for production inference)

Hardware donors receive:
- Recognition in AUTHOR.md and the project README
- Priority support and feature requests
- Early access to new capabilities

Contact: slate.git@proton.me

